# List of regional edge nodes to configure on the central Control Plane.
# Format: node_id,plaintext_token  OR  node_id:plaintext_token
# Note:
#  - Lines starting with '#' and empty lines are ignored.
#  - Pre-shared plaintext tokens are automatically hashed using SHA-256 locally
#    before configuration upload. Plaintext secrets are never uploaded.
#
# Examples:
# us-east-1,my-super-secure-edge-token-us
# apac-singapore:my-super-secure-edge-token-apac
